{"tid":450960,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企要換電視，唔識揀邊部好，求救","createTime":"2017-10-28T16:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T14:28:18.000Z","uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa85eede03c7030d3a53b9aab615499eb705ec2","tid":450960,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身屋企兩老話想買Panasonic th-43ex680h。雖然唔知佢哋點樣得出呢個結論想買呢部，但係我怕會買貴左之餘 我自己又唔識電視嘅野，唯有寄望巴打們幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先講用途，我淨係知道屋企開最多係新聞台，其次就係食晚飯時段嘅愛回家 同埋老豆星期日睇馬<br />\n呀媽想上網睇韓劇(用電視睇),於是覺得需要一部識上網嘅智能電視<br />\n請問  係唔係買部平嘅全高清電視 加啲唔知乜嘢小盒子就可以上網睇劇，平過就咁買一部貴嘅智能4k電視？ <br />\n定係智能電視直接上網方便好多，都值得買<br />\n如果有型號推薦，尺寸需要40-50<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5046c65fce5ffb57891693ad3985324a336903a3","tid":450960,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:50:26.000Z","msg":"睇泡菜劇要買行an既電視機"},{"pid":"05f9e74526cc39f7117e47c4b6c623fbe3003641","tid":450960,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇泡菜劇要買行an既電視機</blockquote><br />\n行Android系統嘅 智能電視 咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9de9ed37189a628eba5072988f250e1acab948","tid":450960,"uid":139538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"買Panasonic th-43ex680h $5100左右 5年保<br />\n<br />\n日本牌子,較有信心"},{"pid":"8c6f0b637e74aff42b3faadac141f07d809dba5b","tid":450960,"uid":10062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買Panasonic th-43ex680h $5100左右 5年保<br />\n<br />\n日本牌子,較有信心</blockquote><br />\n邊到買 比較好"},{"pid":"0a0cd5bada57ac5312